author: kaboomlegoman
title: nice Lego car!
review: So you got a nice car zooming down the street! THIS IS A COOL CAR! Okay done with the silly stuff. This thing has the same design as the thunder raceway cars. Well that's pretty much what a tiny turbo car does. Overall this is a great car and you should get it.

author: geistag
title: Cheap and great!
review: The best TT from 2009 for me at least, i just love the green on black scheme. (pretty rare),the wide black wheels look very agressive and also the top part of the car is very smooth!. Just one small problem with the design of the rear end ,which in my opinion is raised to far off the ground and that makes it look unrealistic,still,it can be easily fixed.
